{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"N3fP4seGYlLj"},"source":["**DATA MODELLING - EXAMPLE - TESS PROJECT (TOI) CANDIDATES DATASET**"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"UCmELZwFYxm2"},"source":["**PURPOSE**:\n","This notebook utilises TESS Projects Candidate data to detect short-period planets which may include sub-neptune candidates.\n","\n","Cleaned data is balanced (SMOTE) and split before the following machine learning (ML)models are applied: Support Vector Classifier (SVC), Random Forest (RF), Light Gradient Boosting Machine (LGBM) and Multi-Layer Perceptron (MLP).\n","\n","**INPUT:**\n","TOI_2025.03.30_22.47.16_cleaned.csv - TOI data as at March 2025\n","\n","**OUTPUT:**\n","Optimised Machine Learning models:<br>\n","- model_LGBM_opt.joblib\n","- model_MLP_opt.joblib\n","- model_RF_opt.joblib\n","- model_SVC_opt.joblib\n","<br>\n","\n","**PROCESSING:**\n","Feature importance via Shapley Additive Data cleaning remove redundant features and instances, calculation of addtional features and transformation.\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":3278,"status":"ok","timestamp":1777627338052,"user":{"displayName":"Suzanne Knight","userId":"13236134929098667911"},"user_tz":-480},"id":"SbwkEV8ugTd7","outputId":"b527ccec-fc1f-4fe9-c19c-6576ba4631cd"},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","output_type":"stream","text":["Drive already mounted at /content/drive; to attempt to forcibly remount, call drive.mount(\"/content/drive\", force_remount=True).\n"]}],"source":["from google.colab import drive\n","drive.mount('/content/drive')"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"A_kJPhCSGQGV"},"outputs":[],"source":["# PYTHON LIBRARIES\n","import warnings # Display warning messages\n","\n","warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n","\n","import calendar       # Convert to names of month\n","import csv            # Reading in CSV files\n","import numpy as np